# BhumiDrishti — Centralized Tool Registry

All AI agent tools (schemas + dispatcher) live in **`backend/services/tools.py`**.

## Architecture

```
services/tools.py          ← single source of truth
  ├── ASSESSMENT_TOOLS     (6)  — GIS/spatial lookups
  ├── COORDINATION_TOOLS   (6)  — assessments, teams, dispatch
  ├── REPORT_TOOLS         (3)  — report data + routing
  ├── CHAT_TOOLS           (12) — assessment + coordination (chat agent)
  ├── ALL_TOOLS            (15) — every tool (report agent)
  └── dispatch_tool()          — unified dispatcher, lazy imports
```

